{"tid":123442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選戰】蕭生料林鄭贏面99.99% 網民歡呼：香港有救","createTime":"2017-02-17T01:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T01:44:20.000Z","uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3248e1c2d3e512bca08ef58ecdc7f0d0df63df03","tid":123442,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"特首提名期在2月14日展開，時事評論員蕭若元（蕭生）昨日在其Youtube頻道「蕭若元：最新蕭析」欄目，上載題目為「林鄭取壓倒性提名票 轉軚機會甚微」片段，預測林鄭月娥手握680、690至710、720提名票，並提到他曾指林鄭勝出的機率是99.99%，四捨五入即幾近百分百。不過，蕭生亦有「燈神」稱號，言論一出即有網民留言「香港有救」，「好希望你今次做燈神﻿」、「蕭生你要繼續燈呀，鬍鬚先有機會，加油！」<br />\n<br />\n片段中蕭生表示，根據多份報章報道，林鄭現時已掌握近400提名票，提到《HK01》估計是400票，《NOW政情》則估計她「坐六望七」，而他是多於600票，「我相信一定600票以上」，而選委會分批交上提名。他又指，即使民建聯聲稱「唔綑綁」，但據聞中聯辦會將已填好的提名表逐一要求民建聯選委簽署，相信沒有人膽敢不簽；他預計曾俊華能取得的建制派提名票，不會在50票以上。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，「葉劉入閘係好重要」，因為只有葉劉淑儀可以令林鄭在第一輪投票中未過半數而未能當選，能證明林鄭得不到建制的整體支持，亦能令林鄭和葉劉互相攻擊，即使第二輪投票林鄭當選，亦會增加其管治成本。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170217/56313823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170217%2F56313823&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=35f290cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170217%2F56313823&h=821a6532\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170217/56313823</a>"},{"pid":"754633ee2f66a5faf7ea813f19685129b2a05170","tid":123442,"uid":19692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee36a3eff451b1d5f27ee9ac824c21f26444fac9","tid":123442,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"多謝燒生，燒生好野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e01db135e15be3d0747cb8e656d94adf7049713","tid":123442,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝燒生，燒生好野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"afc17bfb96c290b40d318e8bb4a72cb755248958","tid":123442,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad8439dfea9b59fab2dd54406a43688faeb2280c","tid":123442,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山！"},{"pid":"cfc98830b241d0dc2bbbabf9526bbebc859ac19f","tid":123442,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解曾俊華做就等於有救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能係胡官呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686130c928edcb553b01e8ce4b2bebf972c04549","tid":123442,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解曾俊華做就等於有救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係膽自大做已經叫有救<br />\n膽自大做就實冇救"},{"pid":"4344f309c60408b3c1158d4b949b22f7d0c59aad","tid":123442,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"點解有討論題材，關我撚事咩票都冇張"}]}